ious.gif" alt="DelIcioUs" width="16" height="16" /></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="intro inlineContent"><span>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>$99.99*</h3>\r\nReg. Price $449.99*<br />With new 2-year contract, other fees &amp; <a href="http://www.dell.com/content/topics/segtopic.aspx/mobile/rate_plans?c=us&amp;cs=19&amp;l=en&amp;s=dhs&amp;%7Etab=3" target="_blank">terms</a> apply.</div>\r\n</span> <a class="btn purchase" href="http://www.dell.com/us/p/mobile-venue-pro/fs"> <span class="c"> <strong>Select</strong> </span> </a>\r\n<div class="intro inlineContent">\r\n<p class="prodDesc">Introducing the definitive Windows<sup>&reg;</sup> Phone 7 experience with a 4.1-inch sliding touch display and full QWERTY keyboard.&nbsp; Features include: <br /><br /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The stunning 4.1-inch WVGA AMOLED capacitive, multitouch display enables easier navigation. </li>\r\n<li>With Office Mobile built in, you can operate on-the-go as seamlessly as you would at the office. </li>\r\n<li>Take your gaming experience on the road with the phone that lets you play games on Xbox LIVE. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="facebookLikeBtn">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="productImages"><img class="productHero" title="Dell Venue Pro" src="http://i.dell.com/das/xa.ashx/global-site-design%20WEB/d71ac950-1a9f-e5d8-a2fa-8b0d9c837753/1/OriginalPng?id=Dell/Product_Images/Dell_Client_Products/Mobility/phones/venue_pro/hero/mobile-venue-pro-black-comp-hero-504x350.png" alt="Dell Venue Pro" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="ui-tabs-nav-container">\r\n<ul class="ui-tabs-nav">\r\n<li class="ui-tabs-selected"><a href="http://www.dell.com/us/p/mobile-venue-pro/pd#Overview"><span>Overview</span></a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.dell.com/us/p/mobile-venue-pro/pd#TechSpec"><span>Tech Specs</span></a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.dell.com/us/p/mobile-venue-pro/pd#Misc"><span>In the Box</span></a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.dell.com/us/p/mobile-venue-pro/pd#RatingsAndReviews"><span>Customer Ratings</span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="Overview" class="ui-tabs-panel" style="display: block;">\r\n<div class="tabFeature inlineContent">\r\n<div class="rightImgContainer"><img title="Ready for work and play" src="http://i.dell.com/images/global/products/mobile-accessories/mobile-accessories-highlights/mobile-venue-pro-design1.jpg" alt="Ready for work and play" />\r\n<div class="leftContent inlineContent">\r\n<h2>Ready for work and play</h2>\r\n<span>You want a smartphone that&nbsp;enables you to stay connected<a class="technote microcontent" rel="technotes:mobile-broadband-service" name="modalPopup" href="http://www.dell.com/mc.ashx?id=technotes:mobile-broadband-service&amp;c=us&amp;l=en&amp;s=dhs&amp;modalwidth=400&amp;modalHeight=150&amp;ovropac=0&amp;modalscroll=yes&amp;modaltarget=div&amp;modaltype=tooltip&amp;position=bottom&amp;title=Important%20Details&amp;flip=false&amp;eventType=rollover"><sup>1</sup></a>,  be productive, and keep in touch with colleagues, friends and family?  Dell Venue Pro&trade; is a do everything smartphone that helps you be more  efficient in how you stay connected and entertained. Seamlessly toggle  between your work and life apps. From your favorite games to keeping up  on Facebook<sup>&reg;</sup>, Twitter&trade;, Gmail and YouTube&trade;, Venue Pro keeps what&rsquo;s most important to you at your fingertips.<br /><a><img style="float: left;" src="http://i.dell.com/images/global/products/mobile-accessories/mobile-accessories-highlights/mobile-venue-pro-design2.jpg" alt="Windows Phone" /></a><br /></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="tabFeature inlineContent">\r\n<div class="leftImgContainer"><img title="For your viewing pleasure" src="http://i.dell.com/images/global/products/mobile-accessories/mobile-accessories-highlights/mobile-venue-pro-design3.jpg" alt="For your viewing pleasure" />\r\n<div class="rightContent inlineContent">\r\n<h2>For your viewing pleasure</h2>\r\n<span>See  the world and your life like never before with the stunning 4.1-inch  WVGA AMOLED capacitive, multitouch display. The large screen allows for  easy navigation and viewing of your email, calendar and Web. Your  photos, videos and movies have never looked better in the palm of your  hand. No more squinting or panning&nbsp;&mdash; see the full width of the Web page  in one glance. And Corning''s high-quality, scratch-resistant Gorilla<sup>&reg;</sup> Glass means your view can stay crystal clear.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="tabFeature inlineContent">\r\n<div class="rightImgContainer"><img title="Your life at a glance with Windows Phone 7" src="http://i.dell.com/images/global/products/mobile-accessories/mobile-accessories-highlights/mobile-venue-pro-design4.jpg" alt="Your life at a glance with Windows Phone 7" />\r\n<div class="leftContent inlineContent">\r\n<h2>Your life at a glance with Windows Phone 7</h2>\r\n<span>Imagine  being able to see everything you care about in a single glance without  ever breaking stride &mdash; an email from a friend or co-worker, appointment  reminders, the score in the game or just the weather and time. Customize  the Live Tiles on your start screen so what&rsquo;s most important to you is  always front and center and easily recognized with a momentary look.  Microsoft<sup>&reg;</sup> Office Mobile built in lets you operate on the go as seamlessly as you would in the office.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="tabFeature inlineContent">\r\n<div class="topImgContainer">\r\n<div class="topImg"><img title="Elegant beauty" src="http://i.dell.com/images/global/products/mobile-accessories/mobile-accessories-highlights/mobile-venue-pro-design5.jpg" alt="Elegant beauty" /></div>\r\n<h2>Elegant beauty</h2>\r\n<div class="bottomContent inlineContent">While  the Venue Pro, with its elliptical, slender form fits comfortably in  your pocket, it&rsquo;s probably the last place it will ever be. Sure, its  large 4.1-inch display, that lets you see everything most important to  you at a single glance, will make it hard to put down. But you&rsquo;ll also  love how it feels in your hand. And just a simple slide reveals the full  portrait QWERTY keyboard, providing a superb viewing and messaging  experience.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 0, 200, NULL, 0, 1);
INSERT INTO `sanpham` VALUES (638, 38, 1, 'LG P525', 'Hỗ trợ 2 Sim 2 sóng\r\nMáy ảnh 2.0 MP (1600x1200 pixels)\r\nĐài FM radio với RDS\r\nNghe nhạc: AAC, AAC+, MP3, WMA\r\nXem Phim: 3GP, MP4\r\nKết nối, Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g, Bluetooth V2.1 với A2DP\r\nỨng dụng xem file văn bản', '0000-00-00', 3389000, 'lg_p525_b.jpg', NULL, 0, 200, NULL, 0, 1);
INSERT INTO `sanpham` VALUES (639, 45, 1, 'Dell XCD28 ', ' Dell XCD28  \r\n- Hệ điều hành Android 2.1\r\n- Máy ảnh 3.2 MP, hỗ trợ quay phim\r\n- Máy nghe nhạc, xem phim MP4/H.264/H.263, MP3/WAV/eAAC+\r\n- Mạng 3G với tốc độ truyền tải 7.2 Mbps\r\n- Chức năng định vị GPS\r\n- Xem file văn bản (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, PDF) ', '0000-00-00', 864000, 'dell_XCD28_b.jpg', '<h2>Dell ra mắt bộ đ&ocirc;i smartphone</h2>\r\n<div class="news_description">H&atilde;ng Dell vừa ch&iacute;nh thức ra mắt hai  mẫu điện thoại th&ocirc;ng minh chạy Android l&agrave; XCD28 v&agrave; XCD35 d&agrave;nh cho thị  trường Ấn Độ.</div>\r\n<div class="new_pro_detail_contet">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Theo h&atilde;ng n&agrave;y cho biết, cả hai mẫu smartphone n&agrave;y đều được hỗ trợ mạng 3G v&agrave; chạy tr&ecirc;n hệ điều h&agrave;nh Android 2.1.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img title="Dell ra mắt bộ đ&ocirc;i smartphone" src="http://images.thegioididong.com/Files/2010/11/17/24523/11_Dell-ra-mat-bo-doi-smartphone.jpg" border="0" alt="Dell ra mắt bộ đ&ocirc;i smartphone" hspace="0" align="baseline" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><span style="color: #0000ff;">Bộ đ&ocirc;i smartphone XCD28 v&agrave; XCD35 </span></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Chiếc <a href="http://thegioididong.com/sieu-thi-dien-thoai-di-dong-dell,san-pham-42-117-45414,dell-xcd28.aspx"><strong>Dell XCD28</strong></a> l&agrave; si&ecirc;u dế giải tr&iacute; v&igrave; vậy m&aacute;y hỗ trợ khả năng lướt web mạnh mẽ, media  player hỗ trợ chơi nhạc, video ở nhiều định dạng kh&aacute;c nhau. B&ecirc;n cạnh đ&oacute;,  c&ograve;n phải kể đến m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cảm ứng LCD 2.8inch, một camera 3.2 megapixel,  bộ nhớ trong 200MB, c&oacute; hỗ trợ thẻ nhớ ngo&agrave;i microSD dung lượng l&ecirc;n tới  16GB, đ&agrave;i FM l&agrave; những th&ocirc;ng số nổi bật kh&aacute;c của <a href="http://thegioididong.com/sieu-thi-dien-thoai-di-dong-dell,san-pham-42-117-45415,dell-xcd35.aspx"><strong>Dell XCD28</strong></a><strong>.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trong khi đ&oacute; bản XCD35 được trang bị một  m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cảm ứng 3.5 inch, c&ugrave;ng những th&ocirc;ng số v&agrave; trang thiết bị giống  như tr&ecirc;n phi&ecirc;n bản XCD28.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ph&iacute;a Dell cho biết, chiếc XCD28 sẽ được  b&aacute;n với gi&aacute; 247 USD kh&ocirc;ng bao gồm hợp đồng với nh&agrave; mạng. Trong khi đ&oacute;,  chiếc Dell XCD35 c&oacute; gi&aacute; cao hơn, 382USD.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Hiện Dell vẫn chưa tiết lộ kế hoạch sẽ b&aacute;n bộ đ&ocirc;i mẫu smartphone n&agrave;y ra to&agrave;n cầu, tuy nhi&ecirc;n dự kiến trong qu&yacute; 1 năm 2011.</p>\r\n</div>', 0, 200, NULL, 0, 1);
